{"tid":911782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地團逼爆東涌　邱騰華指不涉住宿交通不屬違法","createTime":"2018-11-22T07:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T03:36:12.000Z","uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ce949d629c69cf76203bbe328f1b5eab97f95b98","tid":911782,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:24:22.000Z","msg":"港珠澳大橋開通後，引發大批違規內地旅行團湧港，逼爆東涌，民怨四起。商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華今(22日)出席一個活動後指，現有法例規定，如<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">內地旅行團抵港後不涉及安排住宿交通及活動，即使沒有本地導遊接待，亦不屬違法</span></span></strong>，大橋開通首三星期，由最初有很多外地旅行社不了解情況，到旅議會最近調查指，有70%旅行團均有本地導遊安排，當局會繼續與業界溝通合作。 <br />\n<br />\n他又指運房局短期內會安排金巴提供購買來回票服務，可以在總量上作出安排及調節，確保讓東涌居民影響減至最低。 <br />\n<br />\n被問及為何在大橋開通後一個月才計劃在口岸設立臨時商店，邱指大橋通車後需要觀察客量以及來港性質，每星期均會審視情況，他指出五分之一旅客純粹為體驗大橋，未必有興趣去香港其他地方，當局認為東人工島如已準備就緒，旅客可以在東人工島折返。另有旅客選擇在旅檢大樓內逗留，可能需要小食、手信，在店舖未全部開業前，政府跨部門認為可以設立小攤檔，有助旅客不用走到市區。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，他指出中美貿易糾紛持續，政府會密切留意對香港影響，預計明年首季需更審慎，相信情況較今年首三季差，實質情況需要視乎美國會否有進一步行動，不希望關稅額會進一步增加，期望全球貿易都可達致多贏，未來會與商會共研應對方案。"},{"pid":"15499faefa3521025df7c638d631ba65149a56b4","tid":911782,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c821ec1c740f1d839f2771bd091f3a2beeacc87","tid":911782,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:27:25.000Z","msg":"(突發) 傳林鄭上報北京換張建宗　消息：邱騰華接任大熱<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/895085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/895085</a>"},{"pid":"a260d2852d0ffde0fafafb5bd319577b1c4af5a0","tid":911782,"uid":33668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:27:52.000Z","msg":"即係以後外國團都唔駛經香港收錢 香港一豪子都收唔返<br />\n<br />\n真係旅遊(業)天堂呀!"},{"pid":"04ff258fa7e9b9f73600bcb1364a642f432f8cb8","tid":911782,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:39:40.000Z","msg":"安排佢地一落車自由行東涌都已經係一個活動啦柒頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ba359398f9a2e3e1783910241d7b92a23cb4bc","tid":911782,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6f98248513834b33cc59e2cbcc7ebd568bad26","tid":911782,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7754f2e400553d6b37e592eddb3b13d3de717aa2","tid":911782,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:27:58.000Z","msg":"過境後嗰段路唔係交通？<br />\n個關口設咗喺東涌呀？"},{"pid":"9797884f9f3d18391ca7e3a99bacc8e77727e707","tid":911782,"uid":3457,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:30:06.000Z","msg":"總知支那人係香港就唔犯法喇 <br />\n殺人強姦放火都係香港人自找既"},{"pid":"4546e8763a92d14e3ba7395b0508e129acd488e2","tid":911782,"uid":150294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"法例就係唔合理嘅事嘅擋箭牌...."},{"pid":"4ee6274978f25f47d0706e441e21a01a34b25f8e","tid":911782,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁點解決先"}]}